RIBBONS 

Pimiento Butter: 
¼	 cup soft butter or margarine
2	tablespoons sieved pimiento
1	tablespoon mayonnaiee
Blend ingredients. 

Green Pepper Butter: 
¼	cup soft butter or margarine
2	tablespoons finely chopped green pepper
Blend ingredients. 

Spread slice of Merita White Bread with Pimiento Butter; cover with a slice of Merila Wheat Bread. Spread top with Green Pepper Butter and cover with buttered white bread. Press together. Cover with damp tea towel. Chill in the refrigerator 1 hour or longer. Cut crosswise into thin sandwiches. Makes about 24 sandwiches. 